fulltitle: Sylvia Meagher: The JFK Assassination and The Warren Report (1967)
title: Sylvia Meagher: The JFK Assassination and The Warren Report (1967)
_filename: _Sylvia Meagher - The JFK Assassination and The Warren Report (1967).webm
description:
From Pacifica Radio Archives #BB4658
http://pacificaradioarchives.org/recording/bb4658

Sylvia Meagher examines the activities of Lee Harvey Oswald in the Soviet Union and the United States prior to President Kennedy's assassination. She goes on to explain how this information refutes the findings of the Warren Commission.

RECORDED: 26 Jan. 1967. BROADCAST: KPFK, 18 Apr. 1967.

Note: A large variety of audio and interviews of interest to researchers and historians are available from Pacifica Radio Archives, and can be purchased as CDs or digitized for a fee. Please visit their site: PacificaRadioArchives.org.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
